Suspend-To-Idle and Suspend-To-RAM for Google Coral Dev Board #314
  https://github.com/google-coral/edgetpu/issues/314
  sudo sh -c “echo enabled > /sys/class/tty/ttymxc0/power/wakeup” (enabling wakeup on UART1)
  sudo sh -c “echo deep > /sys/power/mem_sleep" (set to Suspend-to-RAM)
  sudo sh -c “echo mem > /sys/power/state” (enter Suspend-To-RAM)
  PM: resume devices took 0.032 seconds
  MNote: ttymxc0 is UART1

